### MCP Streamable HTTP Server Test File
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/mcp
### Content-Type: application/json
### Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

### 1. List all available tools
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tools/list",
  "id": 1
}

###

### 2. Get a random Chuck Norris joke
POST http://localhost:3000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get-chuck-joke",
    "arguments": {}
  },
  "id": 2
}

